{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Piece by Piece</i> is a LITERAL puzzle-platformer where each level is fragmented into puzzle pieces for\u00a0you to traverse through by stitching together the level...<i>piece by piece.</i>\u00a0 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With 100 handcrafted levels, test your logic with increasing difficulty featuring unique mechanics as you progress further into the game. With its relaxing yet engaging vibe, <i>Piece by Piece</i> is perfect for puzzle enthusiasts and platformer fans looking to test out a unique take on the puzzle genre.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249380/extras/The_Basics.gif?t=1740513534\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore unique themes that introduce new mechanics to test your logic as you progress from one puzzle box to the next. Portals, mining, rotating pieces and much more to discover!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249380/extras/Explore_Mechanics.gif?t=1740513534\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hybrid levels combine themes and mechanics into a single level, testing your mastery of each new mechanic. Can you make your way through all 100 levels? Make sure to collect the gold puzzle piece in each level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249380/extras/Mix_Themes_1.gif?t=1740513534\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3249380?t=1740513534","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3249380?t=1740513534","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249380/6593d9bb523c3630b364e1c4e35111747e98f9bc/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740513534","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_i